name: Record Bag
description:
Record Bags come in 2 colours Black and Army Green and they are big to hold:
  • 55×12” LP’s
  • 85 x Album CD’s
  • Small enough to pass as hand luggage. Measurements are – 300mm x 300mm x 200mm
  • Trolley Handle
  • Carry Handles
  • Shoulder Strap
  • Side pockets
  • Zip pocket
  • Velcro flaps
  • Front Pockets
This is a perfect record bag and can be used for all purposes. (Business, travel, storage, etc.) We use ours regularly on short trips and week abroad in Spain. We can also add your own Company/Band logo to the bag at extra cost.
